sentences.english: It was less a hill than a gigantic anvil jumping out of the mountain range.
sentences.chinese: 那座他指着的山更象是一个从山脉里蹦出来的铁砧。

sentences.english: Will investment bankers be plummeting from the windows down on Wall Street?
sentences.chinese: 会有投资银行家头冲下从华尔街的某个窗口蹦出来吗？

sentences.english: When I popped out of the womb.
sentences.chinese: 从子宫里蹦出来的时候。

sentences.english: Do a Google image search for just the word ‘bliss,’ and the first result is the Windows wallpaper.
sentences.chinese: 在谷歌图片中搜索幸福，这个图片会第一个蹦出来。

sentences.english: Purple Qiao and secretly leap out of the Xiao stop extra at their front.
sentences.chinese: 紫俏和暗地蹦出来的阿晓更是拦在了她们前边。
